    <item>
      <title>阿波罗计划将私人财富管理部门亚太区员工数量增加一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/apollo-plans-to-double-asia-pacific-headcount-in-private-wealth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 正考虑增加在亚太地区的招聘，以增加富有客户的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-04/apollo-plans-to-double-asia-pacific-headcount-in-private-wealth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 00:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
